INSERT INTO `wp_comments` VALUES (1,1,'A WordPress Commenter','wapuu@wordpress.example','https://wordpress.org/','','2019-01-09 20:57:48','2019-01-09 20:57:48','Hi, this is a comment.\nTo get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard.\nCommenter avatars come from <a href=\"https://gravatar.com\">Gravatar</a>.',0,'post-trashed','','',0,0),(2,263,'Michele Bergh','Michele@berghconsulting.com','','66.41.196.209','2018-01-13 14:52:16','2018-01-13 14:52:16','This is really a great idea. I have a lot of books on kindle too and just never seem to get around to read them. This will help a lot! Thank you for sharing.',0,'1','','',0,0),(3,263,'Robby','robby@fastlinemedia.com','','24.6.113.20','2018-01-13 18:06:10','2018-01-13 18:06:10','Thanks, Michele! I hope it works for you too. :)',0,'1','','',2,1),(4,280,'Patte Shetler','Shetlerp@uniquesitehelper.com','https://www.uniquesitehelper.com','72.77.52.63','2018-02-14 01:18:07','2018-02-14 01:18:07','This was strangely relaxing until you talked about snow boarding. Then I remembered when I took a lesson ... 8 hours of falling and ending with a face plant  That was the only attempt I made.',0,'1','','',0,0),(5,334,'Michael McCullough','mike94070@gmail.com','','110.77.211.88','2018-03-15 02:31:11','2018-03-15 02:31:11','1.  Enforcing laws does not buy votes for Democrats.\n\n2.  Building mass transport (trains, metros, buses)  fights climate change but does not buy votes.  Taipei had no metro in 1976. Today they have  108 stations and 5 main routes and 2 branch lines. The system carried an average of around 2.10 million passengers per day in March 2016.   In 1976, BART ended in San Bruno. In 2018  BART ends in San Bruno.\n\nYell at me all you want, but you sound more like a conservative every day! Keep up the good work.\n\nLove,\n\nDad',0,'1','','',0,0),(6,340,'Patte','Shetlerp@uniquesitehelper.com','https://www.uniquesitehelper.com','72.77.52.63','2018-03-22 01:47:49','2018-03-22 01:47:49','This cracked me up! Nose crack, clothes optional, distractions and the underwater shot! What did you use?',0,'1','','',0,0),(7,340,'Robby','robby@fastlinemedia.com','','24.6.113.20','2018-03-22 04:13:23','2018-03-22 04:13:23','Thanks, Patte! Really appreciate the comment. :)\n\nI picked up an off-brand action camera and a waterproof housing. It\'s a Xiaomi 4k camera..same brand as my 360 camera. They\'re pretty solid for a not-name-brand imo.',0,'1','','',6,1),(8,372,'Paul Lacey','paul@dickiebirds.studio','https://dickiebirds.studio','92.40.248.148','2018-04-29 20:37:30','2018-04-29 20:37:30','This was really fun to watch and experience the highlights of your trip to the UK. Made. Me smile, laugh and feel very nostalgic. You guys were really really welcome and we hope to see you here again some time. Man you are a real pro with the production levels!',0,'1','','',0,0),(9,372,'Robby','robby@fastlinemedia.com','','24.6.113.20','2018-04-30 15:58:51','2018-04-30 15:58:51','Thanks Paul!! It was a blast hanging out with you and the rest of the Dickiebirds team. Can\'t wait to do it again. :)',0,'1','','',8,1);
